snippet.title: ANIMAL SOUNDS so WEIRD you'll be CONFUSED! - Super FUNNY ANIMAL VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Have you ever heard animal sounds so hilarious and ridiculous?! This is so super funny and weird! This compilation is the most impossible try not to laugh challenge ever! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, pigs, parrots, goats,... scream, make funny sounds and noises,...So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
